Package org.jaudiotagger.tag.reference

Class Summary
GenreTypes Genre list

ISOCountry Represents the ISO 3166-1 Country List with ISO 3166-1-alpha-2 code

Contains an enum of countries, their two letter code and description with additional method to allow an enum to be found by its two letter code or its description.
ISOScript Represents the ISO Script

Contains an enum of script, their four letter code and description with additional method to allow an enum to be found by its four letter code or its description.

PictureTypes Pictures types for Attached Pictures
